{"tid":1082475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷拍中六女生裙底　街頭健身王判160小時社服令","createTime":"2019-03-29T03:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T07:44:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b38b1cd033185f09b26f2911242b1073c6c30ba8","tid":1082475,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329105442012-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190329114226\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329105442012-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190329114226&h=6dd02735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾連奪多屆香港錦標賽冠軍的24歲「街頭健身王」黃煒峰，去年10月在慈雲山搭扶手電梯時從後用手機偷拍18歲中六女生裙底，遭男途人揭發後將裙底影片刪走。黃早前經審訊後，被裁定有違公德罪成，今日(29日)在九龍城法院被判接受160小時社會服務令。 <br />\n<br />\n辯方今早呈上由黃的親友及街頭運動組織創辦人所撰寫的求情信，信件提到黃自學成材，參加海外的健身比賽為港爭光，並憑藉其專業引導邊緣青年重回正軌。辯方重申，被告對香港有貢獻，犯案只一時好奇，現已有深切悔意，冀法庭輕判。 <br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示，有案例指出，偷拍裙底即使初犯也需判處即時監禁，猶幸被告向感化官承認他有犯案，反映他已有悔意，法庭因此決定給他一次機會，判他接受社服令，毋須監禁。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329105442012-0329_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190329114226\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329105442012-0329_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190329114226&h=35ce8e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/bkn-20190329105442012-0329_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fbkn-20190329105442012-0329_00822_001.html&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=2c8b5dad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/bkn-20190329105442012-0329_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c56a86e72598aa2d93023a78a1cab4ebbc06680a","tid":1082475,"uid":88002,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:49:56.000Z","ms